<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA616_03_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema616_03.css" />
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema616_03_0003.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div
      id="app_wrap"
      class="ema616_03_su_0003"
      data-current-page="page_1, page_2"
    >
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 class="flex" data-head="1" lang="y">
          생필품을 담은 직육면체 모양 상자를 드론으로 운반하려고 합니다.
          직육면체 모양 상자의 부피를 구해 봅시다.
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <!-- 기능구현 필요 -->
          <h3 lang="y">
            부피가 1 ㎤인 쌓기나무의 수를 세어 상자의 부피를 구해 보세요.
          </h3>
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="top_box">
              <img
                src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_03_SU/top_box.png"
                alt=""
              />
              <div class="first_box">
                <div class="box_show"></div>
                <div class="wrap_box">
                  <div class="btn_wrap">
                    <button class="btn_plus">-</button>
                    <p lang="y">쌓기나무 개수</p>
                    <button class="btn_minus">+</button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                    <select class="custom_dropdown">
                      <option></option>
                      <!--최초선택데이터 생성 방지용-->
                      <option value="12"></option>
                      <option value="24"></option>
                      <option value="36"></option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="second_box">
                <div class="top_input">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <span lnag="y">쌓기나무의 수:</span>
                    <math-field
                      type="number"
                      data-answer-single="36"
                      text-align="center"
                    ></math-field>
                    <span>개</span>
                  </div>

                  <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                    <span lnag="y">부피:</span>
                    <math-field
                      type="number"
                      data-answer-single="36"
                      text-align="center"
                    ></math-field>
                    <span>㎤</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom_box">
              <img
                src="../../common_contents/img/EMA616_03_SU/bottom_box.png"
                alt=""
              />
              <div class="first_box">
                <div class="box_show box_show2"></div>
                <div class="wrap_box">
                  <div class="btn_wrap">
                    <button class="btn_plus">-</button>
                    <p lang="y">쌓기나무 개수</p>
                    <button class="btn_minus">+</button>
                  </div>
                  <div class="dropdown_wrap">
                    <select class="custom_dropdown">
                      <option></option>
                      <!--최초선택데이터 생성 방지용-->
                      <option value="20"></option>
                      <option value="40"></option>
                      <option value="60"></option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="second_box">
                <div class="top_input">
                  <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                    <span lnag="y">쌓기나무의 수:</span>
                    <math-field
                      type="number"
                      data-answer-single="40"
                      text-align="center"
                    ></math-field>
                    <span>개</span>
                  </div>

                  <div class="input_wrap answer2">
                    <span lnag="y">부피:</span>
                    <math-field
                      type="number"
                      data-answer-single="40"
                      text-align="center"
                    ></math-field>
                    <span>㎤</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- 1page -->

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">쌓기나무의 수를 어떻게 세었는지 이야기해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="po_absolute">
            <div class="input_area">
              <div class="input_wrap">
                <math-field
                  class="textarea"
                  id="inputElement01"
                  type="text"
                ></math-field>
                <ol class="example_box">
                  <li lang="y">쌓기나무의 수를 하나씩 세었습니다.</li>
                  <li lang="y">
                    한 층에 놓인 쌓기나무의 수를 센 다음 몇 층까지 쌓여 있는지
                    세었습니다.
                  </li>
                </ol>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <!-- 2page -->
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
<script></script>
